1
00:00:00,220 --> 00:00:01,940
Hello, Ken.
你好,Ken.

2
00:00:02,070 --> 00:00:03,870
Hi, George.
你好,George.

3
00:00:04,570 --> 00:00:07,620
Have you just been to the cinema?
你刚去过电影院吗?

4
00:00:07,620 --> 00:00:09,900
Yes, I have.
是的,我刚去过.

5
00:00:09,900 --> 00:00:11,420
What's on?
上映什么片子?

6
00:00:11,420 --> 00:00:13,750
'Paris in the spring'.
《巴黎之春》.

7
00:00:13,750 --> 00:00:16,940
Oh, I've already seen it.
噢,我已看过了.

8
00:00:16,940 --> 00:00:20,660
I saw it on television last year.
我是去年在电视上看的.

9
00:00:21,160 --> 00:00:24,990
It's an old film, but it's very good.
这是部老片子,但很好.

10
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:28,170
Paris is a beautiful city.
巴黎是座美丽的城市.

11
00:00:28,170 --> 00:00:30,320
I've never been there.
我从未去过.

12
00:00:30,530 --> 00:00:33,480
Have you ever been there, Ken?
Ken,你去过吗?

13
00:00:33,490 --> 00:00:38,010
Yes, I have. I was there in April.
是的,我去过.4月份我在那儿.

14
00:00:38,020 --> 00:00:41,100
Pairs in the spring, eh?
那是巴黎之春,是吗?

15
00:00:41,140 --> 00:00:43,020
It was spring,
是春天,

16
00:00:43,030 --> 00:00:45,480
but the weather was awful.
但天气太糟了.

17
00:00:45,480 --> 00:00:48,310
It rained all the time.
一直在下雨.

18
00:00:48,480 --> 00:00:51,160
Just like London!
就像伦敦一样!

